<li><a href="http://www.anesi.com/ussbs02.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.anesi.com/ussbs02.htm" rel="nofollow">Summary Report (European War)</a>, U.S. Strategic Bombing Survey, 30 September 1945, retrieved 10 January 2008.</li>
