<li><a href="http://www.timewitnesses.org/english/%7Eangela2.html" class="external text" title="http://www.timewitnesses.org/english/%7Eangela2.html" rel="nofollow">"Angela's Story: Machine-gunning civilian refugees"</a>, <i>Timewitnesses</i>, March 2003, retrieved 10 January 2008.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.learningcurve.gov.uk/heroesvillains/g1/" class="external text" title="http://www.learningcurve.gov.uk/heroesvillains/g1/" rel="nofollow">"Winston Churchill and the Bombing of Dresden"</a>, <i>Heroes and Villains</i> series, British National Archives, retrieved 10 January 2008.</li>
