<li>Furlong, Ray. <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3211690.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3211690.stm" rel="nofollow">"Horrific fire-bombing images published"</a>, BBC News, 22 October 2003, retrieved 10 January 2008.</li>
<li>Hansen, Randall. Fire and Fury: The Allied Bombing of Germany. Doubleday, 2008: <a href="http://www.amazon.ca/Fire-Fury-Bombing-Germany-1942-1945/dp/0385664036/ref=pd_bbs_sr_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1235502026&amp;sr=8-1" class="external free" title="http://www.amazon.ca/Fire-Fury-Bombing-Germany-1942-1945/dp/0385664036/ref=pd_bbs_sr_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1235502026&amp;sr=8-1" rel="nofollow">http://www.amazon.ca/Fire-Fury-Bombing-Germany-1942-1945/dp/0385664036/ref=pd_bbs_sr_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1235502026&amp;sr=8-1</a></li>
