<li>Metzger, Lothar. <a href="http://www.timewitnesses.org/english/%7Elothar.html" class="external text" title="http://www.timewitnesses.org/english/%7Elothar.html" rel="nofollow">"The Fire-bombing of Dresden"</a>, an eye-witness account, <i>Timewitnesses</i>, May 1999, retrieved 10 January 2008.</li>
