urg_in_World_War_II" title="Bombing of Rothenburg in World War II">Rothenburg ob der Tauber</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Rotterdam_Blitz" title="Rotterdam Blitz">Rotterdam</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Saarbr%C3%BCcken#World_War_II" title="Saarbrücken">Saarbrücken</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Salzburg#20th_century" title="Salzburg">Salzburg</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bombing_of_Schaffhausen_in_World_War_II#Schaffhausen" title="Bombing of Schaffhausen in World War II" class="mw-redirect">Schaffhausen</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bombing_of_Schw%C3%A4bisch_Hall_in_World_War_II" title="Bombing of Schwäbisch Hall in World War II">Schwäbisch Hall</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Schweinfurt#World_War_II" title="Schweinfurt">Schweinfurt</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sendai#History" title="Sendai">Sendai</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sheffield_Blitz" title="Sheffield Blitz">Sheffield</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bombing_of_Sofia_in_World_War_II" title="Bombing of Sofia in World War II">Sofia</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Southampton_Blitz" title="Southampton Blitz">Southampton</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bombing_of_Stalingrad_in_World_War_II" title="Bombing of Stalingrad in World War II">Stalingrad</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/History_of_Szczecin#In_the_Third_Reich_.281933-1945.29" title="History of Szczecin">Stettin</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bombing_of_Stuttgart_in_World_War_II" title="Bombing of Stuttgart in World War II">Stuttgart</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/History_of_